{"word":"Esau","slug":"esau","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Esau</b> <a href=\"#/H6215\">H6215</a><br/><a href=\"#/G2269\">G2269</a> <br/> Eldest of twin sons born to Isaac and Rebekah.<br/> Birth of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=26'>Gen 25:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=34'>1Ch 1:34</a><br/> Called Edom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=1'>Gen 36:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=8'>Gen 36:8</a><br/> A hunter<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=28'>Gen 25:28</a><br/> Beloved by Isaac<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=28'>Gen 25:28</a><br/> Sells his birthright for a mess of pottage<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=25&verse=34'>Gen 25:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=39&chapter=1&verse=2'>Mal 1:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=9&verse=13'>Rom 9:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=12&verse=16'>Heb 12:16</a><br/> Marries a Hittite<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=34'>Gen 26:34</a><br/> His marriage to, a grief to Isaac and Rebekah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=35'>Gen 26:35</a><br/> Polygamy of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=26&verse=34'>Gen 26:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=28&verse=9'>Gen 28:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36&verse=3'>Gen 36:3</a><br/> Is defrauded of his father's blessing by Jacob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=27'>Gen 27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=20'>Heb 11:20</a><br/> Meets Jacob on the return of the latter from Haran<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=33&verse=1'>Gen 33:1</a><br/> With Jacob, buries his father<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=29'>Gen 35:29</a><br/> Descendants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=36'>Gen 36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=1&verse=54'>1Ch 1:54</a><br/> Enmity of descendants of, toward descendants of Jacob<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&verse=14'>Oba 1:14</a><br/> Ancestor of Edomites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=8'>Jer 49:8</a><br/> Mount of Edom, called Mount of Esau<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&verse=9'>Oba 1:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&verse=19'>Oba 1:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&verse=21'>Oba 1:21</a><br/> His name used to denote his descendants and their country<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=2&verse=5'>Deu 2:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=8'>Jer 49:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=10'>Jer 49:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&verse=6'>Oba 1:6</a><br/> Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=31&chapter=1&verse=18'>Oba 1:18</a>"}]}